        .mb-14.lg:mb-0
          .rounded-lg.shadow-lg.h-full.block.bg-white
            .flex.justify-center
              .p-4.bg-indigo-600.rounded-full.shadow-lg.inline-block.-mt-8
                = inline_svg_tag "fa-icons/solid/hand-point-up.svg", class: "w-8 h-8 fill-white"
            .p-6
              %h5.text-lg.font-semibold.mb-4 One-time setup
              %p
                It takes about 15mins for your organization IT admin to set up Enough Email. Then, selected colleagues can start creating filters for everyone directly from their inbox.
%section
  .px-6.max-w-screen-md.mx-auto
    %h2.text-3xl.font-bold.mt-20.mb-10 How it works
    %ol.relative.border-l.border-gray-200.dark:border-gray-700
      %li.mb-10.ml-4
        .absolute.w-3.h-3.bg-gray-200.rounded-full.border.border-white.dark:border-gray-900.dark:bg-gray-700{:class => "mt-1.5 -left-1.5"}
        %time.mb-1.text-sm.font-normal.leading-none.text-gray-400.dark:text-gray-500 Step 1
        %h3.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.dark:text-white Admin setup
        %p.mb-4.text-base.font-normal.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
          Someone from your organization who has admin rights on your Google Workplace will need to sign in to Enough Email and follow instructions to set things up. This will take around 15mins.
      %li.mb-10.ml-4
        .absolute.w-3.h-3.bg-gray-200.rounded-full.border.border-white.dark:border-gray-900.dark:bg-gray-700{:class => "mt-1.5 -left-1.5"}
        %time.mb-1.text-sm.font-normal.leading-none.text-gray-400.dark:text-gray-500 Step 2
        %h3.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.dark:text-white Role setup
        %p.text-base.font-normal.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
          Select trusted colleagues who will have permissions to create organization-wide filters. It could be just one person, or everyone at your organization - it's up to you. They will receive an onboarding instruction email.
      %li.mb-10.ml-4
        .absolute.w-3.h-3.bg-gray-200.rounded-full.border.border-white.dark:border-gray-900.dark:bg-gray-700{:class => "mt-1.5 -left-1.5"}
        %time.mb-1.text-sm.font-normal.leading-none.text-gray-400.dark:text-gray-500 Step 3
        %h3.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.dark:text-white Filter
        %p.text-base.font-normal.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
          Whenever a trusted colleague receives an unwanted email, they can forward it to one of the predefined email addresses to block the sender or sender's entire domain for your entire organization - going forward these emails will be automatically archived
      %li.ml-4
        .absolute.w-3.h-3.bg-gray-200.rounded-full.border.border-white.dark:border-gray-900.dark:bg-gray-700{:class => "mt-1.5 -left-1.5"}
        %time.mb-1.text-sm.font-normal.leading-none.text-gray-400.dark:text-gray-500 Step 4
        %h3.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.dark:text-white Review
        %p.text-base.font-normal.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
          You can review who and when created new filters by logging in to Enough Email any time.

